              href="https://github.com/markhorn-dev/astro-nano"
              aria-label="Astro Nano on Github"
              external
            >
              Astro Nano on Github
            </Link>
            to fork the repository, read the docs or one-click deploy on Vercel or
            Netlify.
          </p>
        </article>
      </section>

